
1  Nelo olaiguanani o Haman ilo sirua te nebo Esta enkitok o laiguanani. 
2  Ore te nkolong e are, ina kata eokito enaisho oo sabibu, neitoki olaiguanani ajoki Esta, “Kainyoo eomonunoto ino Esta? Eikinchori iyie. Ainyoo eyieunoto ino? Tenaa ninye kolpisiai le nkitoo ai, naa keitabari.” 
3  Newaliki Esta ajoki, “Tenaa kanoto omom, too nkonyek inono, olaiguanani, naa te neitiship olaiguanani, nchoo maaishori enkishui ai te yieunoto ai, o ltung'ana laainei te nkomono ai. 
4  Amu etimiraki iyiook, nanu o ltung'ana laainei, pee emuti iyiook neari matuata neimisieki iyiook. Tenaa naaji ketimiraki iyiook aaitaa irindiki, ilewa o nkituaak, anaata atigire, amu meitanyaanyukieki osina lang enkitarruorroto to laiguanani.” 
5  Nejoki olaiguanani Serser Esta, “Kaing'ae ilo, naa kaji etii, ilo oitieu ataasa ena?” 
6  Nejoki Esta, “Olaarani naa olmang'atinta ninye; ele arruoni Haman!” Neureishoyu Haman te dukuya olaiguanani o enkitok o laiguanani. 
7  Neinyototo olaiguanani te ilo sirua te ngoro nelo enkurma e ina aji e nkitoo; neton Haman aomonu enkishui enye te Esta enkitok o laiguanani, amu etoduaa ajo eitobirita olaiguanani entorroni naarie ninye. 
8  Neshukunye olaiguanani eing'uaa ina kurma e nkaji e nkitoo elotu ewueji duoo neokie enaisho oo sabibu, ore Haman ina kata ebatata aomonu olng'ur, nebatatakino ina rruat natii Esta; nejo olaiguanani, “Keyieu neikony enkitok o laiguanani te dukuya nanu ti atua enkaji ai, Ore pee epuku ilo rorei te nkutuk o laiguanani neimulumuli enkomom e Haman. 
9  Nejo Harbona obo loo sunaishi oogelema ooisiaai olaiguanani, “Ore ninye ilo shata ogorishoreki ooitobiraka Haman Mordekai, laa ororei lenye oitajeuo olaiguanani, neitasheyieki te nkaji e Haman naa intemat onom enkadoro.” 
10  Nejo olaiguanani, “Entiik elilio ninye te ilo shata.” Neilili Haman te ilo shata ogorishoreki apa oitobiraka Mordekai neyagaa engoro o laiguanani.

